<commentary>hanyād iti māmakyāṃ mātari kāmacittam adhiṣṭhāya pitur akṣobhyasya māraṇaṃ kṛtvā dvābhyāṃ bhakṣayet svadeha evāntar bhāvayet | etenaitad uktaṃ bhavati | krodhādveṣālape jātāmāraṇārthāndhacintakāḥ | na sidhyanti māraṇenaiva krodhabhāvanayā sthitāḥ | kāmayed iti akṣobhyasya sthāne sthitveti bhāvaḥ ||</commentary>
